--- crates/server/src/worker_tasks.rs (core logic, lines 75–135 approx) ---

cap_json_array_tail(obj, key, max_turns) -> bool: truncates JSON array value in map to last max_turns elements; returns whether truncation occurred.

apply_chat_history_cap_on_pull(task_input, max_turns): if max_turns==0 return; if no object or no session_prompt return; cap history and history_assistant; insert history_truncated bool.

build_task_input(job_input, workflow, params, chat_history_max_turns): preserves prior empty-object / chat fallback behavior; if workflow=="chat", runs apply_chat_history_cap_on_pull on result.

finish_pull_response: passes state.config.chat_history_max_turns into build_task_input.

